<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="scroll-smooth" lang="it">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>

<body class="bg-background-light text-slate-800 font-sans transition-colors duration-300">
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

        <section class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12 items-center">
                    <div>
                        <span
                            class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">
                            La nostra storia
                        </span>
                        <h1
                            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight mb-6">
                            Semplifichiamo l'IT per far crescere il tuo <span class="text-primary">Business</span>.
                        </h1>
                        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                            B4US srl è una giovane e dinamica società di consulenza, soluzioni e servizi IT nata con
                            l'obiettivo di supportare le aziende nella loro trasformazione digitale attraverso
                            l'innovazione e l'efficienza.
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
                                <span class="font-medium">Passione per l'Innovazione</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
                                <span class="font-medium">Approccio Pratico</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-0 relative">
                        <div class="aspect-video rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                            <img alt="Team working together in a modern office" class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                                src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDCJH9DjEnEM3lzKhAjTj4f4dUPlbt8d-lQ8L0KDnfrHNhk_eauhear9cOqJoq0qDyPKkFp7xrJUakE3ZxQ8KswsHf6fiHaXre_J_fEIhw10C4QNBD9D9c0fnbOZJfOFDa716Rg9cpOQAM3ChasWBRgYloeT5b6vXvTgGDVE2ZgoKeB5NECOAs661bvpZur5ECX7bIPFdMvUcupQvMnT_qPKAFJUpBhlUC23OC4rW1_WijHpiqec_hPf1OEco0yOMKS5c7cu3XZK6gS" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">I nostri valori fondamentali</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Costruiamo il futuro basandoci su solide fondamenta di
                        integrità e competenza tecnica.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div
                        class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">psychology</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Visione Strategica</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Anticipiamo i cambiamenti del mercato IT per
                            offrire soluzioni che durano nel tempo.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">groups</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Persone al Centro</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Il nostro capitale più grande è il team di esperti
                            che lavora con passione ogni giorno.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">bolt</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Agilità e Risultati</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Rispondiamo velocemente alle sfide complesse con
                            soluzioni pragmatiche ed efficaci.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="py-24">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="mb-16">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Il Team Leadership</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-2">I volti dietro l'eccellenza di B4US.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
                    <div class="group">
                        <div
                            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl mb-4 aspect-[4/5] bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
                            <img alt="Riccardo Germinario - CEO & Founder"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
                                src="/images/Rick.jpeg" />
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Riccardo Germinario</h4>
                        <p class="text-primary font-medium text-sm">CEO &amp; Founder</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="group">
                        <div
                            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl mb-4 aspect-[4/5] bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
                            <img alt="Nicolò Guerra - CTO"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
                                src="/images/nicolo.jpeg" />
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Nicolò Guerra</h4>
                        <p class="text-primary font-medium text-sm">Cloud - Collaboration</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="group">
                        <div
                            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl mb-4 aspect-[4/5] bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
                            <img alt="Pedro Nova - IT Strategy Manager"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
                                src="/images/pedro.jpeg" />
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Pedro Nova</h4>
                        <p class="text-primary font-medium text-sm">Systems</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="group">
                        <div
                            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl mb-4 aspect-[4/5] bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
                            <img alt="Pasquale Schiavone - Head of Innovation"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
                                src="/images/lino.jpeg" />
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Pasquale Schiavone</h4>
                        <p class="text-primary font-medium text-sm">Cloud - Infrastructure</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="py-24 bg-primary relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 border-8 border-white rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
                </div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white rounded-full translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
                <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-16 border border-white/20 shadow-2xl">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-white/40 mb-8 block">format_quote</span>
                    <blockquote
                        class="font-serif italic text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-white leading-snug space-y-4">
                        <p class="mb-4">"Non pretendiamo che le cose cambino, se continuiamo a fare le stesse cose. La
                            crisi può essere una grande benedizione per le persone e le nazioni, perché la crisi porta
                            progressi."</p>
                        <p class="mb-4">"La creatività nasce dall'angoscia come il giorno nasce dalla notte oscura. E'
                            nella crisi che sorge l'inventiva, le scoperte e le grandi strategie..."</p>
                        <p class="mb-4">"La vera crisi è l'incompetenza... Senza crisi non ci sono sfide, senza sfide la
                            vita è una routine, una lenta agonia. E' nella crisi che emerge il meglio di ognuno..."</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-4">
                        <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-white"></div>
                        <cite class="not-italic text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-widest">Albert
                            Einstein</cite>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="py-20">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Pronto a trasformare la
                    tua realtà digitale?</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-10 text-lg">Il nostro team è pronto ad ascoltare le tue
                    sfide e trasformarle in opportunità di crescita.</p>
                <a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full text-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-green-500/30 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1"
                    href="#">
                    Contattaci oggi
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>